      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants a budget-friendly runaround, a handy backup vehicle, or a project to tinker with. It has character, it\u2019s priced to make sense, and for the right buyer it could be a really worthwhile find. If you want cheap motoring without spending a fortune, this one is well worth a look.",
