    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid candidate for an enthusiast build or budget driver with good bones and plenty of upside. The drivetrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of honest mechanical character that rewards a hands-on owner. Not perfect cosmetically and it shows typical wear, but it presents as a usable, restorable platform with a lot of value left in it. If you want an affordable project with real potential, this one is worth a serious look.",
